<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Request for Information (RFI) Notification</title>
  <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
  <!-- Custom Styles -->
  <style>
    /* Customize styles here */
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f0f0f0;
      padding: 10px;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #fff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .btn {
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      display: inline-block;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="text-center mb-4">
      <img src="https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/whiteboard-website.appspot.com/o/assets%2Fimage%2Flogo%2Fwhiteboardtec-logo.png?alt=media&token=f73c5257-9b47-4139-84d9-08a1b058d7e9" alt="Company Logo">
    </div>
    <h2 class="text-center mb-4">Request for Information (RFI) [Sent/Received]</h2>
    <p>Dear [Recipient's Name],</p>
    <p>I hope this message finds you well. This is to inform you that we have recently [sent/received] a Request for Information (RFI) regarding [briefly describe the subject or project].</p>
    
    <div class="card mb-4">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h5 class="card-title">RFI Details</h5>
        <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
          <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Sender:</strong> [Your Name/Organization]</li>
          <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Recipient:</strong> [Recipient's Name/Organization]</li>
          <li class="list-group-item"><strong>RFI Details:</strong> [Provide a brief description of the RFI content or purpose]</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p>Please review the RFI at your earliest convenience and let us know if there are any clarifications needed or actions required on your part.</p>

    <p>Thank you for your attention to this matter. We look forward to your prompt response.</p>

    <p>Best regards,<br>
    [Your Full Name]<br>
    [Your Job Title]<br>
    [Your Company Name]<br>
    [Contact Information]</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
